                    <span class="section-label-modern">WHAT CLIENTS SAY</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title-modern">Testimonials from Happy Customers</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="row g-4">
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <div class="testimonial-card-modern">
                            <p class="testimonial-text">"Excellent service and professional team. They made the entire process smooth and hassle-free."</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <div class="author-avatar">
                                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=100&q=80" alt="Client">
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <div class="author-name">Alex Johnson</div>
                                    <div class="author-title">Home Buyer</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <div class="testimonial-card-modern">
                            <p class="testimonial-text">"Best real estate company I've worked with. Highly recommended for anyone looking to buy or sell."</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <div class="author-avatar">
                                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=100&q=80" alt="Client">
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <div class="author-name">Sarah Williams</div>
                                    <div class="author-title">Property Investor</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
